11:Ta6c,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"What analytics tools do you set up?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"We implement GA4, Google Tag Manager, and Looker Studio dashboards as a baseline. We also set up multi-touch attribution and integrate with your CRM or ad platforms for full-funnel revenue visibility."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How do I know if my current tracking is accurate?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"We start with a full audit of your existing setup: missing events, broken conversions, duplicated tags. We fix all of it before building anything new."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Do you build custom dashboards?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Every client gets Looker Studio dashboards built around their specific KPIs, not templated reports with irrelevant metrics. You get a clean view of what's driving revenue and what isn't."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How long does the implementation take?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"A standard GA4 + GTM setup takes 2–4 weeks. More complex setups with CRM integration, e-commerce tracking, or multi-location attribution take 4–6 weeks. We give you a clear timeline after the audit."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can you connect analytics to my CRM?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. We integrate GA4 and ad platforms with most major CRMs for offline conversion import and revenue attribution. This means you can see which campaigns and channels are actually generating closed revenue, not just leads."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which analytics tools do you work with?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"GA4, Google Tag Manager, Looker Studio, HubSpot, Salesforce, and native ad platform analytics. We build in whatever your team already uses or recommend a fit."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How much does marketing analytics management cost?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Retainers run $1,500 to $3,500 per month depending on channels, integrations, and reporting depth. One-time GA4 and dashboard setup projects start at $3,000."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can you fix our existing GA4 setup?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Most audits we run find missing events, duplicate conversions, or broken CRM connections. Core tracking issues usually clear in 2 to 3 weeks."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Do you report on ROI and ROAS?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, when CRM integration is in place. We report cost per lead, cost per acquisition, ROAS by channel, and pipeline value tied to marketing."}}]}6:[[["$","script","0",{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"@id\":\"https://www.kinexisdigital.com/#organization\",\"name\":\"KINEXIS Digital\",\"url\":\"https://www.kinexisdigital.com\",\"logo\":{\"@type\":\"ImageObject\",\"url\":\"https://www.kinexisdigital.com/assets/logos/KINEXIS_icon_logo.webp\",\"width\":512,\"height\":512},\"description\":\"Digital marketing agency specializing in SEO, paid media, web design, CRO, and analytics for local businesses, SaaS companies, and enterprise organizations.\",\"sameAs\":[\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/kinexisdigital\"],\"contactPoint\":{\"@type\":\"ContactPoint\",\"contactType\":\"sales\",\"email\":\"hello@kinexisdigital.com\",\"availableLanguage\":[\"English\",\"Spanish\"]}}"}}],["$","script","1",{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Service\",\"@id\":\"https://www.kinexisdigital.com/en/services/analytics#service\",\"name\":\"Marketing Analytics Services\",\"description\":\"Marketing analytics services that connect campaigns to revenue with proper GA4 setup, custom dashboards, and multi-channel attribution. Turn data into…\",\"provider\":{\"@id\":\"https://www.kinexisdigital.com/#organiza